Package com.flipkart.business

Interface GymOwnerServiceInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
GymOwnerService
public interface GymOwnerServiceInterface
This interface defines the operations related to gym owners. This includes creating a gym owner, adding gym centers, showing gym centers, and editing slots for gym centers.
